Ne.

1011
02:06:44,995 --> 02:06:46,786
Ne završava se tu.

1012
02:06:50,037 --> 02:06:52,370
Znaš kako ide dalje?

1013
02:06:53,494 --> 02:06:54,953
Da.

1014
02:06:55,828 --> 02:06:57,578
